snippet.title: WWDC 2008 News: Monkeying around on the iPhone
snippet.description: At Apple WWDC 2008 in San Francisco, Ethan Einhorn of Sega shows off a new and improved 'Super Monkey Ball' for the iPhone--complete with 4 monkeys and 110 stages.
